@title Welcome to nosh
@doc <code>nosh</code> (nosql shell) is a Bourne shell emulator implemented in Erlang.

When finished, the <code>nosh</code> application will augment Bourne shell functionality
with a UNIX-style Erlang command set and the ability to mount CouchDB databases to the
file system.
@end